cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.LG 

This paper deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis of code-mixed tweets, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also uses machine learning techniques for classification, which can be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The topic of the paper, demonetization, is related to social and information networks (cs.SI) and the dataset used in the paper can be considered as a resource for social media analysis (cs.SD). Finally, the paper deals with language modeling and code-mixing, which can be categorized under computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CY).
